Mistakes covered over in yellow or blacked out; some corrections and additions in margins; some folios treated with yellow turmeric powder.

msIdentifier.repository: Kislak Center for Special Collections, Rare Books and Manuscripts

msContents.summary: Manuscript is used by priests or householders for consultation about the rules and regulations (Hindu law, Dharma) governing rites that are to be performed on specific lunar days (tithi) of the Hindu calendar. Small segmented diagram/graph with various individual Bengali characters in most of the segments (f. 62v).
